OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy day with bright
OL,6,For sunny spells at times. Showers will
OL,7,Fbe scattered and mostly restricted to
OL,8,Fthe west before becoming leas frequent
OL,9,Ffrom the late afternoon. Breezy in the
OL,10,Fwest and north.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FBright spells with the odd
OL,13,Fevening shower, these mostly in the
OL,14,Fnorth, becoming cloudy with some
OL,15,Fpatchy rain spreading north later.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FMostly cloudy with patchy
OL,18,Flight rain in the morning. A band of
OL,19,Fwidespread and occasionally heavy rain
OL,20,Fwill spread northeast during the
OL,21,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
