OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,6,FOutbreaks of heavy rain pass northeast
OL,7,Fduring Sunday. This will be followed
OL,8,Fby bright or sunny spells and showers,
OL,9,Fsome heavy, through the rest of the
OL,10,Fperiod.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
